startups.name: Nativo Digital
startups.product_desc:
After launching the first on-site, beginner-focused coding bootcamps in Latin America through World Tech Makers, we decided to scale our passion in a fun way - through education and video games.

We launched Nativo Digital's Alpha and after 3 weeks, we had over 2,700 users testing our platform. We are launching the Beta within the next months.

We use artificial intelligence, leverage gamification and trends like mobile and web technology in a region that is emerging and has enormous potential: the Americas. We focus on Portuguese, Spanish and English speaking populations aged between 5 and 40 years old. Our platform is adaptive: it adapts to the user by identifying strengths, weaknesses and preferences through gamified concepts, stories and processes. We teach highly valuable skills - coding skills - and aspire to allow our users to become technology creators.
startups.high_concept: Nativo Digital is a web and mobile adaptive and gamified technology education platform.

How it Works?

1.	Post a project for free. 
2.	Receive offers, compare and hire the best talent. 
3.	Release the payment when the project is completed successfully.

What are the benefits?

startups.name: Mi Kit
startups.product_desc:
Each period cycle, women deal with the hassle of buying feminine care products: lines at the store, not finding what they are looking for, traffic, stress, missing important work or personal events, etc.

Mi Kit is a subscription-based online retailer of feminine care products based in Colombia. We offer a new shopper experience to help our customers buy the products they need in a convenient, discrete and personalized way. Our value proposition:

1) Convenient: We remind you when to re-order. You receive your kit at home, no need to go to the store.

2) Discrete: Your kit arrives in a beautiful discrete box.

3) Personalized: You can build your own kit according to your needs.

4) Trustworthy: You can order an emergency kit anytime, we'll deliver it within 40 minutes (in available locations)

5) Easy to use: USer-friendly website, easy to build/modify your kit and to reorder. Mobile app also available.

6) Surprise gifts with your kit every month

startups.name: Pikabook
startups.product_desc:
Pikabook gives higher education students access to every book they are asked for during their studies through their pc, laptop and smartphone. It's easy, affordable and legal.

Academic books face a big problem in Latin America. They are expensive and students almost always need only a few chapters of them. This leads them to go for the easiest solution: photocopies.

Both governments and publishers have tried to fight against book piracy, unsuccessfully. It has proven to be a problem very hard to control in Latam. We believe the solution is not trying to end with illegal photocopying, but to give students an alternative. This is how Pikabook is born.

Pikabook goes with the promise "forget about photocopies", offering students an option to pay a monthly fee for complete access to the digital academic books of their need.

Product: Digital platform for academic books.
Customer: Higher education students.
Helps: To have access to their academic readings without the need of photocopying.

startups.name: Big Media Consulting
startups.product_desc: Con el surgimiento de nuevas tecnologías nace el Big data como una forma de conocer el comportamiento del consumidor digital. Es de esta manera que notamos una necesidad puntual dentro del mercado Latinoamericano donde las marcas no saben aprovechar todo el potencial que se obtiene a través del análisis de datos, ni crear estrategias basadas en el comportamiento del consumidor digital (de hecho siempre se crean estrategias para obtener datos y no al revés), es ahí donde aparece lo que nosotros llamamos Big Media. Esto no es precisamente ningún avance tecnológico, en cambio se convierte la manera en la que trabajamos para dar a nuestros clientes soluciones reales para las necesidades de su target, creando estrategias basadas en métricas reales que permitan dar ejecución y solución a necesidades puntuales de los consumidores.
startups.high_concept: Del Big Data al Big Media sí hay mucha diferencia.

startups.name: farma.social
startups.product_desc:
FARMA.SOCIAL: "The right medication in the right place at the right price". Is a set of tools to enable patients/customers, retailers and pharmaceuticals to interact and provide the best services and price to patients/customers in the right place at the right price.

In the pharma (for OTC and prescription drugs ) business there is a big opportunity for end customers and retailers and also pharmaceuticals. For the first ones Farma.Social help them to locate the better price/service deals (related to location, price, and also to service in the point of sale). For retailers, opens a new opportunity to compete in the market being open about service and pricing so the customers can decide. Finally for pharmaceuticals, our solutions provides new and effective means to be more attached or close to their customer's needs, to know them better by compliment their supply/distribution chains and marketing strategies towards the right locations and markets.

startups.name: Whooptag
startups.product_desc:
http://whooptag.com

Whooptag is a free service that lets you feel and experience shared moments in social networks as if they were yours, as if you were there.

Through Whooptag's social search engine, search for words, people, or topics of interest, and, quickly and in real-time, discover moments related to your search captured by other people on various social networks, and immerse yourself into a complete experience, in one place.

With Whooptag you can :

- Search the content you want in real time, without having to be a user of the selected social network, and without being a follower of the person you search for.

- Experience shared moments in different social networks in one place.

- Find similar content to what you search for through related tags.

See what your favorite artist, player or celebrity is chatting about in different social networks, or what fans are saying about them. Discover whatever you want at Whooptag.

Shows results from twitter , instagram and youtube.

startups.name: nutrio
startups.product_desc:
Our big choice is to develop a platform named NUTRIO, using technology and the help of caregivers, mainly teachers and family members, to register and geolocalize malnutrition data of the 12 million kids between 0 and 12 years old and improve their eating habits. These caregivers are our target users. We plan to have a pool of partners like, doctors, NGOs, government institutions and the private sector, who produce children related services.

NUTRIO makes it easier and more attractive for caregivers to register and record the nutritional and vaccine data of the kids under their protection. We are also thrilled about the chance to achieve a geolicalized national data base for decision makers to make best nutritional policies for children, and achieve goals like the Millennium Development Goals.

Parents of all over the world would be able to track their sons nutritional and vaccine data, supporting the use of Nutrio in development countries.

It’s a platform that seeks to solve symmetry of information and reduce transaction cost in the sports market of soccer pitches. By locating an available and near pitch in the city map and letting the user to book a pitch in advance. 

As well, Fut5App through a gamification process tries to create a unique experience and promotes competence that motivates soccer players and users to interact, this by creating teams, promoting and participating in leagues and tournaments.  Fut5App is a club. On the other hand, Fut5App helps the owner of the pitch to manage his/her income by counting daily, weekly and monthly bookings with its price into charts and web reports. It is very useful to manage pitch's commercial and accounting strategy. To sum up, Fut5App responds to the soccer fans requirements for playing, by booking in pitches managed by their owner, in a easier, more convenient way for satisfy both needs.
